---
/**
 * ProblemSection - "Why Now?" with timeline and HNDL diagram
 * Creates urgency about the quantum threat
 */
---

<section class="problem-section not-content">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 class="section-title">Prepare for the Quantum Era</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">NIST has finalized post-quantum standards. Governments target 2030 for migration.</p>

    <div class="problem-grid">
      <!-- Card 1: 2030 Deadline -->
      <div class="problem-card fade-in">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.2"/>
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="22" stroke="#FF55A3" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="100 40" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <text x="24" y="28" text-anchor="middle" fill="#FF55A3" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter, sans-serif">2030</text>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>The Deadline</h3>
        <p>NIST, NSA, and major governments target <strong>2030</strong> for post-quantum migration. RSA-2048 and ECC will be deprecated.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Harvest Now Decrypt Later -->
      <div class="problem-card fade-in">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
            <rect x="4" y="20" width="16" height="12" rx="2" stroke="#FF55A3" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <path d="M12 20V16a6 6 0 0112 0v4" stroke="#FF55A3" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="26" r="2" fill="#FF55A3"/>
            <path d="M24 26h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 3" opacity="0.3"/>
            <rect x="28" y="20" width="16" height="12" rx="2" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.6"/>
            <path d="M36 24v4" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.6"/>
            <circle cx="36" cy="24" r="1.5" fill="#ef4444" opacity="0.6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Harvest Now, Decrypt Later</h3>
        <p>Adversaries are <strong>already collecting</strong> encrypted data. When quantum computers arrive, they'll decrypt everything.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Standards Ready -->
      <div class="problem-card fade-in">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
            <path d="M14 24l6 6 14-14" stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="20" stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Standards Are Ready</h3>
        <p>NIST finalized <strong>FIPS 203, 204, 205</strong> in 2024. The algorithms exist. The tools exist. Time to act.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline -->
    <div class="timeline fade-in">
      <div class="timeline-line"></div>
      <div class="timeline-point" style="left: 0%">
        <div class="timeline-dot active"></div>
        <span class="timeline-label">2024</span>
        <span class="timeline-desc">NIST standards finalized</span>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-point" style="left: 33%">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <span class="timeline-label">2025</span>
        <span class="timeline-desc">Early adopters migrate</span>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-point" style="left: 66%">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <span class="timeline-label">2028</span>
        <span class="timeline-desc">Industry mandates begin</span>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-point" style="left: 100%">
        <div class="timeline-dot danger"></div>
        <span class="timeline-label">2030</span>
        <span class="timeline-desc">Classical crypto deprecated</span>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-progress"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .problem-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .problem-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(0, 91, 197, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .card-icon {
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-4);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .problem-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .problem-card p {
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .problem-card strong {
    color: var(--sl-color-accent-high);
  }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding: 2rem 2rem 3.5rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .timeline-line {
    position: absolute;
    top: 2rem;
    left: 2rem;
    right: 2rem;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-5);
  }

  .timeline-progress {
    position: absolute;
    top: 2rem;
    left: 2rem;
    width: 15%;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF55A3, #005BC5);
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .timeline-point {
    position: absolute;
    top: 2rem;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Adjust positions to account for padding */
  .timeline-point:nth-child(2) { left: calc(2rem) !important; }
  .timeline-point:nth-child(3) { left: calc(2rem + 33% * (100% - 4rem) / 100%) !important; left: 33% !important; }
  .timeline-point:nth-child(4) { left: 66% !important; }
  .timeline-point:nth-child(5) { left: calc(100% - 2rem) !important; }

  .timeline-dot {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    border: 3px solid var(--sl-color-bg);
    margin-top: -6px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .timeline-dot.active {
    background: #FF55A3;
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(255, 85, 163, 0.5);
  }

  .timeline-dot.danger {
    background: #ef4444;
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
  }

  .timeline-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
  }

  .timeline-desc {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-4);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* Light mode */
  :root[data-theme='light'] .problem-card {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .problem-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .problem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .timeline {
      display: none;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
